Package hu.bme.mit.theta.xsts.dsl.gen

Interface XstsDslListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
XstsDslBaseListener
public interface XstsDslListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by XstsDslParser.
